title.rendered: Tesla Model 3 Is Coming to Indonesia!

content.rendered:
The newest of the Tesla models will be coming to Indonesia soon! Tesla Model 3 is ready for pre-order and is only available at Prestige Motorcars.

There are a range of different options you can choose from, view them below!

Type of Tesla:

Mid Range Battery

Rear Wheel Drive 

Long Range Drive

Dual Motor All-Wheel Drive

Performance

Dual Motor All-Wheel Drive

Colour Option

– Solid Black

– Pearl White Multi Coat

– Midnight Silver Metallic

– Deep Blue Metallic

– Red Multi Coat

Wheel Options

– 19″ Sport Wheels

– 18″ Aero Wheels

Interior Options

All Black

Black and White

Included:

Premium heated seating with 12-way, power adjustable front seats

Center console with covered storage, 4 USB ports and docking for 2 smartphones

Premium audio system

Tinted glass roof with ultraviolet and infrared protection

Auto dimming, power folding, heated side mirrors

Custom driver profiles

LED fog lamps

Premium Connectivity (1 year included):

Satellite maps with live traffic visualization

In-car streaming media

Over-the-air updates via Wi-Fi & cellular

Premium heated seating with 12-way, power adjustable front seats

Center console with covered storage, 4 USB ports and docking for 2 smartphones

Premium audio system

Tinted glass roof with ultraviolet and infrared protection

Auto dimming, power folding, heated side mirrors

Custom driver profiles

LED fog lamps

Premium Connectivity (1 year included):

Satellite maps with live traffic visualization

In-car streaming media

Over-the-air updates via Wi-Fi & cellular

Prices for each model start from:

Mid Range Battery:           IDR 1,475,000,000 

                                             DP 442,500,000

Long Range Battery:         IDR 2,500,000,000

                                             DP 750,000,000

Performance:                   IDR 2,700,000,000

                                            DP  810,000,000

*Prices are off the road. Prices on the road are subjected to goverment regulations.

Customise Your Tesla Model 3 how you want and experience the world of electric vehicles. 

All Tesla model 3 vehicles will receive 2 year warranty included.

The cars will be available as soon as June of 2019! Order your Tesla Model 3, pay a downpayment of 30% now and enjoy it within 6 months!
